<item>
<title>Inspirational Stores : Creating &amp; Sharing Value, Delivering Profit and ROI Thru e-Commerce !</title>
<link>http://micheldeguilhermier.typepad.com/mdegblog/2008/12/inspirational-stores-delivering-profit-and-roi-thru-ecommerce-.html</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true">http://micheldeguilhermier.typepad.com/mdegblog/2008/12/inspirational-stores-delivering-profit-and-roi-thru-ecommerce-.html</guid>
<description>Following my previous post on Aston Martin&#39;s redundancy plan, I believe that in the present and coming environment, no one is safe or recession-proof. We know that the big 3 US car manufaturers are in (very) serious trouble, we know...</description>
<content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;Following my previous post on Aston Martin&amp;#39;s redundancy plan, I believe that in the present and coming environment, &lt;strong&gt;no one is safe or recession-proof&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We know that the big 3 US car manufaturers are in (very) serious trouble, we know Renault is as well, and most other &amp;quot;volume manucturers&amp;quot; as well, but the news is now that &lt;strong&gt;one of the most iconic luxury car company is also affected, and in a hard way and has tio lay off 1/3rd of its workforce&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bottom line : no company should be arrogant enough&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;to believe it will be unaffected.&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;This is simply sheer lunacy.&lt;em&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sure, some fast growing companies will continue to grow fast (many e-commerce companies are in this case, Inspirational Stores included), but not as much as they would have in a somewhat more positive environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In order to minimize the impact of recession, I strongly believe it&amp;#39;s better to work in a frame of &lt;strong&gt;value-managed relationships&lt;/strong&gt; with one&amp;#39;s partners, be it suppliers or customers. The point is to work closely with partners in a transparent, candid and collaborative way in order to create &lt;strong&gt;whatever value&lt;/strong&gt; there is to create ! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The point today is not to aim one&amp;#39;s guns at others, negotiate hard to pull whatever existing value on one&amp;#39;s side at the expense of the other, but &lt;strong&gt;to work jointly to&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;create value, then to share it in a fair way&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Create value&lt;/strong&gt; in working hard jointly with one&amp;#39;s economic partners, &lt;strong&gt;then share it&lt;/strong&gt; : this is I guess a win/win approach which makes lot of sense these days.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is why I believe &lt;strong&gt;Inspirational Store&lt;/strong&gt;s is perfectly positioned for the coming months : we have a very transparent and &lt;strong&gt;value-oriented approach&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;. &lt;/em&gt;Our genuinely innovative model intrinsically creates value and tightly ties up and aligns both partners&amp;#39; interests in maximizing sales and profit of the e-commerce channel.&lt;em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In other words, thanks to our significant financial means (€13M capital raised) and our very extensive state-of-the-art e-commerce infrastructure and expertise, ranging from in-house technology team to e-marketing, customer care and logistics, &lt;strong&gt;I believe we are better position than anyone else to deliver economic performance and profit&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;to our partners, through e-commerce&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt; ! &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sure, no denying we need to work hard to sell to consumers who are now more budget-conscious,&lt;strong&gt; but our e-commerce performance-based proposition is simply of tremendous value to our partner&lt;/strong&gt;s, be it &lt;strong&gt;Ladurée&lt;/strong&gt; in the food segment, &lt;strong&gt;Lamarthe &amp;amp; Delvaux&lt;/strong&gt; in handbags, &lt;strong&gt;Antik Batik&lt;/strong&gt; in the woman apparel business or &lt;strong&gt;Kot&lt;/strong&gt; in the weight loss food (new partner for us, I&amp;#39;ll tell more about in another post).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ultimately, our goal is to establish the e-commerce channel as the most profitable channel for our partners and deliver them an excellent return on their internet investment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Should you have &lt;strong&gt;great ambitions&lt;/strong&gt; for your brand online, feel free to get in touch with &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:mdeguilhermier@orange.fr&quot;&gt;me&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;I usually react in less than an hour to any email !&lt;em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded>


<category>Inspirational Stores</category>

<dc:creator>Michel de Guilhermier</dc:creator>
